sentences.en: Any calls made to you or Casey Becker are being cross - referenced.

sentences.en: But Casey and Cole are not impressed with their mother's publishing success.

sentences.en: Casey added that everything he had told us was, of course, top - secret.
sentences.cn: 凯西补充说,他告诉我们的话当然全部是绝密的.

sentences.en: Casey Becker and Steve Orth were killed last night.
sentences.cn: 凯西·贝克尔和史蒂夫·厄斯昨晚被杀了.

sentences.en: Casey has been on a course of sewing all this month.
sentences.cn: 这个月凯西一直在上缝纫课.

sentences.en: Casey replace Tom to give oneself up to the government.

sentences.en: Casey slept well, was quiet and always behaed in public.

sentences.en: Casey Stengel was probably the most colorful character in baseball.
sentences.cn: 凯西·施滕格尔可能是棒球界最有趣的人物。

sentences.en: Did you happen to ride by Casey Becker's house?
sentences.cn: 你是否正好就兜到凯西·贝克尔的家了?

sentences.en: Here Mr. Casey had placed at my disposal the agreeable villa he was using.
sentences.cn: 这里,凯西先生把他自己居住的那座舒适的别墅供我自由使用.

sentences.en: I'm sorry, Casey, I didn't mean to snap at you like that.
sentences.cn: 对不起，凯西，我不是有意要跟你凶的。

sentences.en: If Casey is correct, the total cost of the cleanup would come to $110 billion.
sentences.cn: 如果凯西是对的，清理的总花费将达1,100亿美元。
